title: [Tiervah's Outfitting]
[Tiervah's General Store]
description: Beneath a woven seagrass ceiling, a silken sea-themed tapestry hangs on one of the blue-speckled sea glass walls.  A long mistwood counter and a pink-edged open clamshell sit in opposite corners while some puffed raw silk pillows rests on a woven seagrass floor.
